Package: cups
Version: 1.1.14
Revision: 1
Maintainer: Max Horn <max@quendi.de>
Depends: libjpeg-shlibs, libpng-shlibs, libtiff-shlibs, zlib
BuildDepends: libjpeg, libpng, libtiff
Source: mirror:custom:%v/cups-%v-source.tar.bz2
CustomMirror: <<
 nam-US: ftp://ftp.easysw.com/pub/cups/
 eur-FI: ftp://ftp.funet.fi/pub/mirrors/ftp.easysw.com/pub/cups/
 eur-DE: ftp://ftp.mpg.goe.ni.schule.de/pub/internet/printing/cups/
 eur-GR: ftp://ftp.ntua.gr/pub/gnu/cups/
 eur-TR: ftp://ftp.fisek.com.tr/pub/cups/
<<
SourceDirectory: cups-%v
Patch: %f.patch
ConfigureParams: --disable-ssl --mandir='${prefix}/share/man'
SetCFLAGS: -I%p/include
DocFiles: *.txt LICENSE.html
Description: Cross-platform printing solution
DescPackaging: <<
This package doesn't use splitoffs on purpose, at least for now - in 10.2,
Cups will be integral part of the system, and it's doubtful whether we
want to keep on providing our own cups package then.
<<
DescPort: <<
* fixed shared lib builiding on OS X
* fixed their quirky configure script - required so that the package honors
  the prefix parameter for make install
<<
Homepage: http://www.cups.org
License: GPL/LGPL
